edu.ncsu.csc316.hr.util

Class MySplayer

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.ncsu.csc316.hr.util.MySplayer

  • public class MySplayer
extends java.lang.Object
    MySplayers class is an implementation of a splay tree It has the methods of insert, getYears, getDegree, delete, exists, and splayer. It is used to make a tree by reading in the dictionary and to extract values from it
    Author:
    Islahuddin Arshad
